en both men finished just ahead of Parchment in the final of the event at the National Championships in June.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 787, \"end\": 795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.8680751519636599, \"rank\": 0.15197399411531703, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Broadbell\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2022 Commonwealth Games champion\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"Bennett\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"the obstacle event\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"their time\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"both men\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 878}, {\"ngram\": \"Parchment\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"the National Championships\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parchment, who has a personal best of 12.93, is ranked the 18th-fastest man over the distance this year.\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parchment\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"the 18th-fastest man\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"the distance\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Grant Holloway of the United States is the quickest man globally this year with 12.86.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Holloway\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grant Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hollo